# secret detection blacklist rules
# format: rule_id|regex
aws_access_key_id|AKIA[0-9A-Z]{16}
github_pat|ghp_[A-Za-z0-9]{36,}
github_fine_grained_pat|github_pat_[A-Za-z0-9_]{20,}
openai_api_key|sk-[A-Za-z0-9]{20,}
slack_token|xox[baprs]-[A-Za-z0-9-]{10,}
private_key_begin|-----BEGIN (RSA|EC|DSA|OPENSSH|PGP) PRIVATE KEY-----
generic_password_assignment|([Pp][Aa][Ss][Ss][Ww][Oo][Rr][Dd]|[Pp][Aa][Ss][Ss][Ww][Dd]|[Pp][Ww][Dd]|[Ss][Ee][Cc][Rr][Ee][Tt]|[Aa][Pp][Ii][_ -]?[Kk][Ee][Yy]|[Tt][Oo][Kk][Ee][Nn])\s*[:=]\s*['\"][^'\"]{8,}['\"]
